overview:
Guest Blog It is an awesome place to find free guest blogging websites and bloggers in all niche markets online. Start building the awesome back links that you have always desired today.

The company was founded originally by Chris Burns in January of 2012. Then, in February 2012, a new owner was added to the company, Whitney Segura, age 23.

Whitney Segura is an entrepreneur internet marketer from Lafayette, Louisiana United States. He specializes in eCommerce and search engine optimization, as well is skilled in team building and outsourcing.

Chris Burns is a social media marketing and networking specialist, he has been running a company called Burns SEO, which provides online marketing services and web design to clients.

Guest Blog It was founded and built for one reason, to create a higher quality guest blogging network and better advertising opportunities for publishers.

Sign up for free today at http://www.guestblogit.com/membership-options-page, and start publishing instantly!

Affiliate marketers should sign up at the newly launched affiliate program for Guest Blog It, offering 25% commission on monthly $20 subscription costs, for the duration of the account.

To become an affiliate, go to http://www.guestblogit.com/idevaffiliate/.
